    "This approach allows us to generate a perturbed input text embedding that leverages the most significant features from the original text embedding.",
    "Finally, we calculate the energies (or frequencies) for each perturbed sample using Algorithm 1 and 2, average them, and utilize the aggregated energy to optimize the loss function.",
